{"tid":499214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女司機撞完警車 疑即日再撞的士","createTime":"2017-12-14T14:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T13:39:28.000Z","uid":56533,"like":649,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"de6e5346b8eae4840563735448fa7dd1ae8820c3","tid":499214,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vLNIVfVVG21b9pQH7L2Ceg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/ca07346fbb3d2a5d2959ee2b30057674\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvLNIVfVVG21b9pQH7L2Ceg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fca07346fbb3d2a5d2959ee2b30057674&h=5bb33962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小姐，乜又係妳呀？昨日（13日）有女司機於大埔四線轉彎唔夠位直撼警車，惹起網民熱烈討論，未料事件仲有下集！有網民上載另一段車Cam片，顯示該車同日再「出招」，硬撼的士車尾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據該車Cam片段顯示，一輛黃色私家車昨日(13日)上午九時許，沿大老山隧道往九龍方向行駛，車輛正於收費亭前慢駛排隊，準備付款，豈料該黃色私家車疑收掣不及，撞向的士車尾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細看車牌，該車正是同日上午八時許在大埔撞警車的黃色車。換言之，該車一小時內先撞警車，再撼的士，令人嘖嘖稱奇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據警方資料，昨日驅車撞向警車的，為一名女司機。雖然未知在收費廣場「再下一城」的車手是否為同一人，但網民已經議論紛紛，直斥其駕駛技術「恐怖」、「真係唔明點解會考到牌」、「岀色女車手」等。亦有網民笑指該司機應被釘牌，降低香港車禍率。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%88%E4%BF%82%E5%A6%B3%E5%91%80-%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%92%9E%E5%AE%8C%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A-%E7%96%91%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E6%92%9E%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB-094152683.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%2588%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A6%25B3%25E5%2591%2580-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%25AE%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2592%259E%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB-094152683.html&d=A1ULU37iwBzk0xgqJ3kRS%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fe74a884\" target=\"_blank\">